Iga '''Aḥidus''' yan wurar art skarn [[imaziɣen]] n [[Aṭlas anammas|waṭlas anammas]] d [[Asammr|Usammr]]. Iga urar ẓḍarn att skrn ifrxan ula tifrxin, ar tettemziriy talɣa nns zɣ tmnaḍt ar tayyaḍ. Zikk, ar ttaɣn imaziɣn n tmnaḍin ad aḥidus ɣ kraygat tizi, lumaṛ ad day zrint tinwutci, mac tigira ad ar tettggan ɣar ɣ tmɣriwin d tfugliwin. Skrn kra n tmsmunin kra n trubba ganin aḥidus d tazzult ar sis ttetkkan timizar akk ar sis drrunt ɣ inmuggarn d igdudn n umaḍal.

